---
// src/components/infopages/ThankYou.astro
// Frontmatter simplificado para evitar errores de compilación
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-zinc-950 text-white min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
  <div class="relative z-10 px-8 md:px-12 2xl:max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <span class="text-lime-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.5em] mb-6 block">
        SISTEMA ACTUALIZADO
      </span>
      
      <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl lg:text-[13rem] font-black uppercase tracking-tighter italic leading-none">
        GRACIAS
      </h1>
      
      <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
        <p class="text-zinc-500 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Tu mensaje ha sido interceptado exitosamente. Un estratega de <span class="text-white font-bold">VANTTA</span> se pondrá en contacto contigo en breve para iniciar la fase de escalamiento.
        </p>
        
        <div class="pt-8">
          <a 
            href="/" 
            class="inline-block border border-white/20 hover:border-lime-400 px-10 py-4 text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-all duration-500 hover:text-lime-400 bg-white/5"
          >
            REINICIAR INTERFAZ
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-lime-900/20 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="w-full h-full bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/carbon-fibre.png')] opacity-20"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Aplicamos el grosor y estilo solicitado */
  h1 {
    font-weight: 900 !important;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
</style>